item.title: Rice University Lecture Notes (Mathematics and Physics)
Competitive Physics Notes (Olympiad Training)
item.description: Practicing Physics Problems for Olympiads was a large part of my middle school and later high school career, and I had written several handouts back then. Their quality is rather questionable but I hope to re-rewrite some of them when I take the relevant physics courses.
